summary: Adds more flora to Winterhold to take care of those pesky unrealistic open areas
descriptionHtml:

Description

Adds more Trees and other flora to Winterhold (mostly pines because of the location). I thought there was a lot of empty spaces in this town this fixes that ^.^


Requirements

Skyrim (of course :P )
